track.name: I'll Survive
comments: Love the king. and he is the King.
Such a good singer and this song. Wow
Anything that BB King does is simply superb authentic blues!
Prob. one of the best songs on the Blues on the Bayou disc. Not too bad really considering it's one of his newest works.

i am sorry... the two first shouts in this lineup just make me laugh.
i love this song... BB is so awesome... especially his later work... he is so relaxed and natural... so pure and just perfect... that is all :-)
saw him in San Diego last night and he was great!!!
toujours grandiose, le papy du blues, toujours autant d'énergie dégagée comme le feu du volcan.
I'd like to inject something else into you
this man has a way with the guitar that injects life into my soul
